Stone, William C. - The Wall Street Transcript













































 





































William C. Stone
William C. Stone founded SS&C Technologies Holdings, Inc., in 1986 and has served as Chairman of the board of directors and Chief Executive Officer since SS&C’s inception. Prior to founding SS&C, Mr. Stone directed the financial services consulting practice of KPMG LLP, an accounting firm based in Hartford, Connecticut, and was Vice President of Administration and Special Investment Services at Advest, Inc., a financial services company.
